com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.edrs

Class ContextResultMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.edrs.ContextResultMapping

  • public final class ContextResultMapping
extends Object
    A mapping that associates the results in an ExternalDataContextResults or an ExternalDataContextItemsResults with the ProvenanceGroup that contained the CardProvenance that matched them.
    Since:
    4.0

    • Constructor Detail

      • ContextResultMapping

        public ContextResultMapping(String provenanceGroupId,
                    Collection<String> contextItemKeys,
                    boolean complete)
        Constructs a new ContextResultMapping.
        Parameters:
        provenanceGroupId - A String that contains the identifier of the ProvenanceGroup to which this ContextResultMapping refers.
        contextItemKeys - Strings that contain the keys from the ItemIdentifiers of the Items in the results to which this ContextResultMapping refers.
        complete - true if the ExternalDataContextResults or ExternalDataContextItemsResults that contains this ContextResultMapping is a complete set of results; false if the result set is incomplete because a maxNumberOfItems parameter was exceeded.
